description.plain:
“I Like the Way You Kiss Me” by Artemas, is a blend of futuristic pop with hints from the moody 80s era, characterized by pulsating synths and a dark, retro-futuristic sound.

Artemas brings his gloomy, crooning vocals to the chorus, creating a contrast to the track’s overall kinetic energy. The lyrics depict a narrative of a troubled relationship where the protagonist is uncertain about the status of the relationship.

Ultimately, he admits to prioritizing physical intimacy over emotional connection by emphasizing the importance of sex in the relationship.

The track went immediately viral via social media such as TikTok, amongst other platforms, which helped Artemas emerge into the scene of music industry.
